snippet.title: Party Arcade - Pre-Order Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order your copy of Party Arcade now and be ready to party on October 23, 2018! 
Pre-order Now ► http://www.partyarcadegame.com/

From the creators of multi-million selling Game Party Champions, Party Arcade is the latest family-friendly party game exclusive to Nintendo Switch. Grab up to three friends online or sit them on the couch and compete in classic, all-time favorite carnival games!

Follow us on
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/PartyArcadeGame/
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/PartyArcadeGame
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/partyarcadegame/
